main event: A dark gray object, about the size of a jet plane with no wings, was observed moving from east to west in 1961.
interesting points: The object moved at a high speed and disappeared behind a house.
The witness stated the description of the object was very similar to one observed a few weeks earlier on January 7, 1961.
The witness is an active member of a UFO club and claims to have information from reliable sources about a real UFO sighting over Boston in April 1961.
The witness is a strong supporter of UFO research and has studied the subject for years.
The object was observed for about 1 minute.
